teacheasy.data

Class PageObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.data.PageObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnswerBoxObject, AudioObject, GraphicObject, ImageObject, MultipleChoiceObject, TextObject, VideoObject

    public abstract class PageObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the data that describes a Page Object as defined in the TeachEasy digital lesson XML format. Extended by all the various page object types.
    Version:
    1.0 05 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Alistair Jewers
